name: Rise & Shine Muesli
description:
Rise and shine muesli 
Natural muesli means you can start the day with a spring in your step and keep that right through until lunch. Eat it as you fancy: as a muesli, bircher muesli or porridge. No added sugars, the only sweetener is the real fruit inside!

name: Beautiful Bean Stew
description:
We think this is the perfect all-round summer salad and winter warmer. Ready to cook - all you need to do is add water, boil and serve. 

A tangy tagine without spending hours waiting for the flavours to take hold. Spices, dried figs and beans will be transformed into a Moroccan feast in minutes (well, about 60 minutes!) . Ideal on it's own or with your favourite fresh ingredients. Of course you can always pop in some fresh herbs, tomatoes and even a little bit of feta if you fancy an extra treat! 
Contains up to 8 (yes, really EIGHT) servings!
